author: Anonymous Gear
title: Problem set 1 107 vs 110 autograder
question:
Hi there,
I am currently registered in the waitlist for 110 while also registered in 107 in case I do not get a spot in 110. 
I noticed that my autograder cooldown for problem set 1 is the same between both classes (I am unable to see feedback for the 110 pset1 right after submitting pset1 for 107).
While I do not mind waiting for the cooldown, I am concerned whether my pset1 for 107 will somehow interfere/ replace my pset1 for 110 or vice versa.
Could someone look into this for me?
Thank you
instructor_answer: The cooldown applies on a per assignment basis, and psets/pset-01 is different from 107/psets/pset-01
